description:
Higashikata Jousuke is the main protagonist of http://anidb.net/a11734 [Diamond Is Unbreakable].
Jousuke is a high school freshman residing in the town of Morioh. Part IV begins as Joutarou Kuujou searches for him on behalf of Joseph Joestar, Jousuke`s aging, absent father.
name: Higashikata Jousuke
